<!--SearchStart//-->
<h1>43. A stroll around Goytre Hall Wood</h1>
<div class="article-video right clearfix"/>
<p/><div>
<span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">This small, gently undulating broad-leaved woodland is set amongst a flowing landscape of farms, small fields and woods.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Further Information</strong></span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">There are seats and picnic tables next to the car park. A 200 metre long stone-dust path leads from the car park to a pedestrian gate at the boundary hedge. A rough track leads from the gate to the canal centre at Goytre Wharf, 400 metres away. This track can be muddy during the winter and after rain.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>How to get there:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">The wood is close to the A4042 between Abergavenny and Pontypool, 1.5km north of Penperlleni and 2 km south of Llanover. Follow the sign by the bus stop for Goytre Wharf and the car park is on the right hand side after 300 metres.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Nearest town or village:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Penperlleni.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>OS Grid Reference:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Explorer Map OL 13 or Landranger Map 161- SO 317 062.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Distance</strong>:</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Up to 200 metres of easy surface, with another 400 metres along a rough track.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Contact</strong>:</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Monmouthshire County Council on 01633 644856.Â Â Â Â Â  Â </span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Facilities</strong>:</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">The nearest facilities are at Goytre Wharf and in Penperlleni village.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Parking:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">There is space for 8 cars on the compacted stone-dust surface car park.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Toilets:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">The nearest toilets are at Goytre Wharf Canal Centre.</span></span></span><br/>Â </div>

